merge - Merges two files (typically galaxies)... 

./merge <galaxyA> <galaxyB>

where galaxyA.data and galaxyB.data are your files

================================

alter - rotates, translates, or kicks a galaxy data file

./alter galaxyA rotate 45 60 70  //x axis rotate, y axis rotate, z axis rotate
./alter galaxyA translate 10 0 0 //same axes
./alter galaxyA kick 0.1994 0 0  //same axes

assumes the typical 

M	X	Y 	Z	Vx	Vy	Vz

Form . . .

===============================

addBlanks

adds blanks (massless velocity-less particles at 0,0,0) 
such that CUDA reads data in multiples of 256, simplifies the code :)

./addBlanks galaxyA 368
adds 368 massless particles



